tafsir[9]{c,v,t}:
  42,23,"Ko ngon welo-welo mawngo, woni ko Allah wewlinirta jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, e junngo Nulaa…ìe Makko on; …ìen jeyaa…ìe gom…óim…ìe Allah e Nulaa…ìe Makko …ìen, …ìe golli golle mo∆¥∆¥e. An Nulaa…óo, maaku: mi …óa…ì…ìiraa on njo…ìdi woo, e ko mi yottinta kon, si wanaa njo…ìdi wootiri, ndi nafitorton onon; ndin woni: nde yi…óorton lam, fii ko mi en…óam mon. Kala faggitii…óo mo∆¥∆¥ere, Men …ìeydanay mo njo…ìdi e hoore mayre: mo∆¥∆¥ere nden, ko sappo yeru mayre. Pellet, Allah ko Haforoowo junuubi kala tuubu…óo e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, mantoowo golle ma…ì…ìe mo∆¥∆¥e …óen …óe …ìe gollirta fii Makko."
  42,24,"Hini jeyaa e ko sirkoo…ìe …ìen aa∆¥ii, wonnde Muhammadu (yo o his) fefindi ndee Alqur'aanaare, o dammbi nde e Joomi makko. Allah ruttiiri …ìe wiide: hara a aru fefindaade fenaande woo, Ma Mi notu e …ìernde maa nde, Mi meha meere fefindaande nden, Mi heddina goonga kan. Nde tawnoo non, wanaa non woniri, …óum tinndinii wonnde Annabiijo on (yo o his) ko wahayu Joomi makko o wonndi e mun. Pellet le, ko O Anndu…óo ko woni e …ìer…óe jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen. Huunde suu…óaaki Mo e mum."
  42,25,"Ko Kanko Allah woni ja…ìoowo tuubuubuyee jeyaa…ìe Makko yeddu…ìe …ìen, si …ìe ruttike e Makko, O yawtana …ìe bon…ói …ói …ìe faggitii …óin, e hoore Himo anndi kala ko huuwoton. Huunde suu…óaaki Mo e golle mon …óen. Ma O yo…ìitoy on …óe."
  42,26,"Himo jaabina toraare gom…óim…ìe Allah e Nulaa…óo Mun on, …ìe golli golle mo∆¥∆¥e, O …ìeydana …ìe e ko …ìe lamndaaki mo kon, ka …ìural Makko. Yeddu…ìe Allah e Nulaa…óo Mun …ìen non, hino woodani …ìe lepte sa…ótu…óe, habbitii…óe …ìe √ëalnde Darngal."
  42,27,"Si tawno Allah ya√±√±anno jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen fow arsike, ko pellet, …ìe bewirayno too√±e ka hoore leydi; kono Himo jippinira arsike on, emmbere ko O muuyi ya√±√±ude O …ìillina. Pellet, ko O humpitii…óo fii jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, Reenu…óo …ìe. O okkiray √±e√±∆¥al Makko ngal, O …ìillinira ngal kadi."
  42,28,"Ko Kanko woni jippinoowo ndiyam …óam e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, …ìaawo …ìe ta∆¥aade fii majjam, O saaka …óam ndiyam, …óam fu…óina leydi ndin. Ko Kanko kadi woni Gi…óo heftu…óo fii ma…ì…ìe, Yettinii…óo e kala fiyaakyu."
  42,29,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji tindinay…ói e kattal e gootaagu Makko ngun: tagugol kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, e …óin ruugay…ói haawnii…ói, …ói O saakiti hakkunde majji. Kanko e fii moo…ìindiroygol …ìe ngol √±aawa …ìe yo…ìita …ìe, nde O haaji e mun woo, ko O hattan…óo. O ronkataa fii mun, wano woniri O ronkaano tagugol …ìe ka arannde laawol."
  42,30,"Kala ko he…ìi on, onon …ìee yim…ìe, immorde e musiiba wonkiijii mon maa e jawle mon, ko sabu geddi …ói juu…óe mon …óen faggitii. Allah non, hino yaafoo ko …óuu…ói e mun, hara O nanngitirtaa on …óin."
  42,31,"On wonaa hattan…ìe laawagol lepte Joomi …óen, si O faandanike on …óe; On maraa kadi yawti Mo Kanko, woni gi…óo hettoowo fii mon, wanaa ballo faabotoo…óo on e lepte Makko …óen, si O faandanii mon …óe."